Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.66,0:00:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me. Today I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.13,0:00:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, filthy demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:01:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer! Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:01:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swimsuits!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's swim, Okumura!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumo, get changed, come on! Put on your bikini!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Come on, come on, hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to help with this crappy squid fry thing when there's all these hotties out there...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come come, have some! This fried squid is so good you'd sell your soul for a single bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be enjoying yourself, Okumura.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well... I don't mind doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not a single customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird. This squid really tastes great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells nyammy too. Just a little... Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:02:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't, it's for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, is that your new familiar cat sith?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They called this a mission so I brought him along...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how's this a mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though this is still better than looking for seaweed for anti-demon drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This shop and the inn we're staying at are both run by the family of the whiskers guy's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to feel like Bon and Koneko were lucky to get away with looking for ghost stones at the Tama river.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about around there by the rocks?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it seems quiet over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we'd need a cute sales girl to attract customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe if Izumo helped out a bit more...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really sucks at teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look cute in your bikini today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:04:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? I helped with the squid fry already, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you think that being a salesgirl suits me better?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swam enough already, so just have your fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I will. We decided to take turns, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same as ever... Even this heat doesn't melt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thanks for your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the business? I'm so happy to have kind students like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teamwork my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this feels good...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too many things have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eek, my leg cramped!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:05:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow! Don't fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was trying to give you mouth-to-mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You touched my breast and assaulted me, how dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I helped you! Show some gratitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mean, you boulderhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one to talk! Look at my forehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My chin is even...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, kiddo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not "kiddo"! I'm Yohei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were really lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But where's your heroic savior?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're so short that I didn't notice you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! My dad said a guy can be small if he's big down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Cut that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's wrong with having a big heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that ruckus about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the sea turns black,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a demon the size of a hill will appear
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and destroy the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been known in these parts for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gods help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:07:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The priest of this temple drew this about 400 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A squid monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The black stain in the sea is probably the ink of the squid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is just a legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, about six months ago the sea turned black,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a man went out to the sea to face the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just our luck to run into demons even here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be great if defeating that thing was our first mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you go earlier? We were worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nowhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nowhere? Anyway, you're really a boulderhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.71,0:07:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw us coming, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would it hurt to stand aside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to. My dad said a man should always walk straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a figure of speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you get lost all the time if you always walked straight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, you wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys know where the pet shop is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pet shop! The directions are written down on this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to show the way to a local?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you always shop there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but my dog can't take this heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's usually your dog leading the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really have no sense of direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna brag, but my dad was even worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He totally had no sense of direction at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:09:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that bragging? You're always going on about your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a great dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sailed out about six months ago, and he hasn't come back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still chasing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It? You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you talking about...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The demon of the sea! It caught my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm gonna defeat it for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your hard work today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raw squid, squid ramen{soumen}, squid soup...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fermented squid and pasta with squid ink? It's all just squid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, but... it's all squid stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might sound fishy, but lately the fishers have only caught squid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So much that we're thinking of invading other markets with it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:10:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why the fried squid isn't selling at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kraken?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a demon of the sea that spits out ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to historical records from Norway, there have been cases where the whole sea turned black from the kraken's ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.02,0:10:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there's only squid left in the sea because of this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it's a kraken, how can we defeat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually the fatal verse of the demons of the sea is Ephesians 1:18.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have limited resources here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's definitely not something a child could handle alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again? But of course, my little kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something came up, so I have to leave you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow we'll have real part-timers in the shop, so you can rest then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:11:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Real part-timers? Then were we just fill-ins?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that "kitty" thing again, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But hey, Okumura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go swimming tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to say that tomorrow you'll have to look after Yohei so that he won't go after the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An ointment. My dad always has this with him to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It works right away, just put it on the bruise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came here just for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, which way is it to my house?{how bad is this kid sheesh...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the sea again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again... That kid must've seen it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind as long as he's not doing anything stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? After all, he saved me once...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I hate people who don't know their limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says that we don't need to take over for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unusual for Izumo to care about someone so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to sit there on the lookout all night, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait forever if I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's really a demon, you won't be able do anything against it on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It's my dad's enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm gonna defeat it for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that there are things that you can't do alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just looking at you makes me feel embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fool who doesn't know his place and who'll only get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'd just run away if you were about to get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad told me that if someone's being all negative it's because the person has no self-confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They try to make others lose their way too because they're lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? You're annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm angry, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if you lose your way, just don't lose sight of what you've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he decided to meet that demon, and he went through with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I won't hesitate either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like my dad, I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yohei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the demon! And it's spitting ink!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, just say your mantra!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a mantra, it's a hymn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you want to fight it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we let it, it might leave the sea and attack the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we have to do something before that kid does!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the riches of the glory of his inheritance in the saints,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and what is the exceeding greatness of his power to us-ward who believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the working of his mighty power...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't work at all! Can a squid hear at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, it has those huge ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every kid knows those are fins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fins? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.96,0:16:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! It's just like a monster movie!{cf gojira}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Blackie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that, Blackie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cats get...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackie! What's wrong? Blackie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cats get sick if they eat raw squid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he? Did he come this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Did he get lost again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've no choice, I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I humbly call upon the Gods of Harvest{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Izumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't summon them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okumura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're crazy! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.37,0:18:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't something a kid can handle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Don't get in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat him and avenge my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell, at this rate I'll have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yohei! Yohei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yohei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whiske{\fscx250}- {\r}Mr. Tsubaki! Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking up stuff because we'd have to take special measures
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if it really was a kraken, but I figured we were in no danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that I didn't know the way home,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so for six months I lived on uninhabited islands or drifted on my raft.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for Japan with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His sense of direction is even worse than mine.{is this supposed to be funny?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, wasn't that the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yohei, you have to open your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understood it when I was fighting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His heart is just as soft as his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's changed a lot for the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if a man once decided to defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! Yohei, keep your heart as clear as raw squid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It takes a man's courage to change your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men are like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, I think I've learned a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Yohei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a great ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demons can have a change of heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to teach you that. It was worth calling you here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just made that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.11,0:22:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to see us off?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.45,0:22:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.58,0:22:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dog got better?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.04,0:22:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. His name's Snowy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.63,0:22:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's cute, right? With those eyebrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.50,0:22:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eyebrows?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.30,0:22:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Eyebrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.63,0:23:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.33,0:23:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you laughed so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.94,0:23:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else could I have done? This was all so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got that right...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.38,0:23:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.33,0:23:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.15,0:23:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An amusement park?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:23:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you finally feeling like playing with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.63,0:23:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, nice, you're cute, Moriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.05,0:24:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that skirt a bit too short?
