Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.97,0:01:10.98,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,rikai mo sezu osaetsukeyou to shitekita
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:14.85,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,ano otonatachi to onaji jan ka yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.85,0:01:19.94,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,doushitatte kanawanai esoragoto darou ga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:24.44,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,mune wo moyasu hi wa dare ni mo keseya shinai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.65,0:01:29.70,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,sora kara furu kuroi ame ga kono mi nurashi furitomanakutomo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.70,0:01:35.12,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,mada ore wa kawareru jibun de kaetemiseru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:40.59,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}kore ga sou "pride" sorezore no basho de
