Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:50.39,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,mada mada ikeru zo ikeru zo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.19,0:00:37.56,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,After birth, people live as they wish
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:40.19,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,They then learn the black box in their head; is that bliss?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:42.74,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Just cross over, beyond the line of your limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:45.70,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, take a step, and I mean this minute
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:50.99,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Life's a bitch, so if it's easy, you're doing it wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.99,0:00:56.12,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, which way is the world going? Then ignore it and go wherever (here we go)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.12,0:01:00.88,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things I could never have, things with time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.21,0:01:05.47,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a reason I force my heart upon them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.97,0:01:10.98,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I never tried to understand, I just forced it on them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:14.85,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no better than those lifeless adults
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.85,0:01:19.94,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's just a pipe dream I could never have
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:24.44,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one can put out the fire in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.65,0:01:29.70,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The black rain may pour hard and leave me drenched
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.70,0:01:35.12,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,But I know I can change, I will change myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:40.59,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}This is my pride, what makes up my core
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.09,0:01:44.92,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,15)}I won't let my fire be put out; not yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:50.39,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep going, and I'll never stop
